---
import PhoneFrame from './PhoneFrame.astro';
---

<section class="py-24 sm:py-32 px-5 sm:px-8 section-divide">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold sm:text-center mb-4 tracking-[-0.02em] reveal">
      How it works
    </h2>
    <p class="text-text-secondary sm:text-center text-[15px] leading-relaxed max-w-xl sm:mx-auto mb-12 reveal stagger-1">
      A lightweight Rust agent runs alongside Claude Code on each machine. Your phone connects directly over LAN or Tailscale. Self-hosted, open source, no third-party servers.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 reveal stagger-2">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-bg-card border border-border hover:border-border-light transition-colors">
        <div class="text-primary font-mono text-xs mb-3 tracking-wider">01</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Install the agent</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">One binary, zero dependencies beyond tmux. Runs on macOS and Linux. Menu bar app for Mac, systemd for servers.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-bg-card border border-border hover:border-border-light transition-colors">
        <div class="text-primary font-mono text-xs mb-3 tracking-wider">02</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Connect from anywhere</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">Same Wi-Fi works instantly. Tailscale gives you secure access from anywhere: coffee shop, commute, couch. Encrypted end-to-end.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-bg-card border border-border hover:border-border-light transition-colors">
        <div class="text-primary font-mono text-xs mb-3 tracking-wider">03</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Scale across machines</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">Run agents on your laptop, your workstation, your server. Marmy shows every machine and every session in one place.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-text-secondary sm:text-center text-[15px] leading-relaxed max-w-xl sm:mx-auto mt-10 reveal stagger-3">
      This isn't read-only monitoring. Spin up new sessions, browse any file on the machine, and kick off work from your phone. Full control, not just a window into what's already running.
    </p>

    <!-- Machines screenshot -->
    <div class="flex justify-center mt-12 reveal stagger-4">
      <PhoneFrame
        src="/screenshots/landing.png"
        alt="Marmy Machines screen showing MacBook Pro, Rpi5, Mac Mini, RpiZero, and EC2"
        class="w-[270px] sm:w-[300px]"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
